name: Jelly Car Worlds Level
summary: A JCWLVL file is a game level used by JellyCar Worlds , a physics-based driving and puzzle game developed by Walaber and published by Disney. It is a renamed Zip-compressed archive that stores the data for a specific level in the game, including the layout of platforms, obstacles, backgrounds, and other elements that make up the course. The JCWLVL format helps keep JellyCar Worlds gameplay consistent and make it behave across platforms as designed.
